snippet: Omaha was chosen to host the final round of the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, the first major international volleyball event outside of the Olympics to be held in the United States.
lead_paragraph: Omaha was chosen to host the final round of the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, the first major international volleyball event outside of the Olympics to be held in the United States.
